    <section class="trust">
        <h2>Trusted by Thousands of Customers</h2>
        <p>Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust CarWashPro for their car’s interior detailing. Our team guarantees excellence, using high-quality, safe cleaning solutions.</p>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 CarWashPro. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer> 
